Package com.example.bot.spring

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Booking
    The class Booking is used when the customer starts a booking.
    Customer
    The class Cutomer models a the customer behavior and stores the information(user ID and customer history) of a customer.
    Discount
    The class Discount is an observer in the observer pattern.
    Filter
    The class Filter can search the tours which fulfill the criteria provided by the users.
    KitchenSinkApplication
    The class KitchenSinkApplication is the main class.
    KitchenSinkController
    The class KitchenSinkController is the controller class of MVC model to respond to customer and regulate our functional classes
    KitchenSinkWebMvcConfigurer
    The class KitchenSinkWebMvcConfigurer manages the configuration of the program.
    NotifyingCustomer
    The class NotifyingCustomer is an observer in the observer pattern.
    PaymentReminder
    The class PaymentReminder is an observer in the observer pattern.
    Report
    The class Report can create and write a txt file which includes the useful questions and feedback from the customers.
    TextHandler
    The class Text Handler is a subject work in mediator pattern.
    TimeManager
    The class TimeManager is a subject in the observer pattern.
    UpdateRecord
    The class UpdateRecord can allow employee of the companey update the payment data of customer, set discount event or ask for question record from customer.
